data.description: Beautiful 2 Story Home in the Heart of Naperville!  Open floor plan features tons of natural light and vaulted ceilings in family room!  Huge kitchen features tons of cabinet space along with SS appliances!  2 story family room features gas fireplace and leads out to huge screen room!  3 bedrooms all upstairs along with 2.5 baths!  Basement is ready to be finished with all of your ideas! Attached 2.5 car garage with fenced in backyard!!
